data.enText: to make sb/yourself familiar with or aware of sth

data.chText: 请把这事的实情告诉我。
data.enText: Please acquaint me with the facts of the case.

data.chText: 你首先需要熟悉文件归档方法。
data.enText: You will first need to acquaint yourself with the filing system.

simple_means.memory_skill: ac 加强 + quaint 知道 → 使〔人们〕知道 → 告知

ex.chText: 时间如有变更，我们将尽快通知你们。
ex.enText: We will inform you of any change of time as soon as possible.

ex.chText: 我们很高兴地通知你，你被聘用了。
ex.enText: We are glad to inform you that you have been hired.

ex.chText: 老师会把该学生取得的任何进步都告诉其家长。
ex.enText: The teacher will inform the parents of any progress the pupil has made.

synonyms.bx: 指将事情或信息正式地告知某人。

ex.enText: You need to acquaint me with the truth.

ex.chText: 她得告诉新老板公司近来的动态。
ex.enText: She has to acquaint her new boss with recent happenings in the company.

ex.chText: 她想知道你有哪些长处以及不足。
ex.enText: She wants to acquaint herself with your strengths and weaknesses.

synonyms.bx: 指将某事告知某人，通常用于 acquaint sb with sth 结构。

ex.chText: 如果地址有变，请尽快通知我。
ex.enText: Please notify/inform me of any change of address as soon as possible.

ex.chText: 他们接到通知，说会议被取消了。
ex.enText: They were notified/informed that the meeting was canceled.

synonyms.bx: 指正式地或由官方通知某人某事，常可与 inform 换用。

example: Please acquaint your colleagues of your plans to move
you should acquaint yourself with your new computer
We familiarized ourselves with the new surroundings

tr: cause to come to know personally
example: permit me to acquaint you with my son
introduce the new neighbors to the community

value.def: If you acquaint someone with something, you tell them about it so that they know it. If you acquaint yourself with something, you learn about it.

example.ex: ...efforts to acquaint the public with their rights under the new law...
example.tran: 为使公众熟悉新法律所赋予的权利而作出的努力

example.ex: I want to acquaint myself with your strengths and weaknesses.
example.tran: 我想知道你有哪些长处以及不足。

trans: 告诉；报告；禀报；让…熟悉；使…熟悉

partsOfSpeech.dec: ac 加强 + quaint 知道 → 使〔人们〕知道 → 告知
acquaint 告知 + ance 状态，性质，状况 → 熟悉；熟人

partsOfSpeech.d: 奇特的，古怪的（人们想要知道怎么回事）
